I've made this map cause i was bored...

I worked like 3 weeks on it and it taked a long time to work on the details.

there are about 16 traps to activate and some breakfloors between the traps.


the idea is:

how further you have come, how scaryer it becomes.


i hope you enjoy it, and pleas make a comment because if you have seen a bug or somthing that isnt good, i will look at it and maby i will change it ;)
